{"tid":2241321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PandaMart標錯價變1折！深夜湧進千筆訂單　超市存貨不足 外送員在店外乾等","createTime":"2020-10-13T08:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T14:01:37.000Z","uid":209657,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5a5e50ecffef73d7ac7c585a495214d495027a","tid":2241321,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/09/2816887-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F09%2F2816887-PH.jpg&h=f728fb88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網友在臉書社團貼出一張照片，台南一間商店外，擠滿了foodpanda的外送員，外送員與機車擠到正常馬路上。原來foodpanda在台南推出24小時「熊貓超市」，商家標錯價，一折出售，深夜湧進千筆訂單，但商家無預警取消所有人訂單，外送員只能在商店外，進退兩難。<br />\n<br />\nPandamart熊貓超市是foodpanda官方經營的線上商店。台南首間主打24小時出貨的「熊貓超市」，因系統標錯價，如容量1858m的統一瑞穗鮮乳，原價約179元，網上只賣25元；930ml的罐裝瑞穗鮮乳，原價85元，網上標價也僅16元，網友爭相走告、瘋狂下單。<br />\n<br />\n不過後來許多訂單遭到無預警取消，超市人員拒不出貨，外送員得知系統出包後，擔心遭客人負評，不敢輕易離開現場，只能茫然乾等。直到公司方出面解釋，請外送員別再等待，早點休息，公司會與現場夥伴溝通取消訂單，所有現場等待的外送員，也都可以獲得該單報酬加倍的補償。"},{"pid":"a52e619f4f7d90683c20f15b9442195b48f9e303","tid":2241321,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/09/2816888-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F09%2F2816888-PH.jpg&h=64d00f4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83e0ece0f5ac78cc200274d394c393f685e925f4","tid":2241321,"uid":209657,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/09/2816889-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F09%2F2816889-PH.jpg&h=a55ed08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台南市主任消保官馮祺雯表示，「如果說契約已經完成，也就是說消費者已經下訂、完成付款，那foodpanda公司就有履約的義務。」<br />\n<br />\n對此，foodpanda發出聲明，強調所有訂單都依約出貨，因為商品存貨不足，不得不取消部份訂單，已經向100多位受影響的消費者致歉，提供全額退款及補償券，外送員也會取得相對應的報酬，也會優化系統，避免狀況再次發生。<br />\n<br />\nfoodpanda資深經理郭昕宜表示，「針對取消的訂單部分，我們除了全額退款之外，也會致上補償券，向消費者道歉。那外送夥伴的部分呢，所有外送夥伴，在現場等待的時間，我們都會加發報酬。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然foodpanda提供補償，不過消保官強調，如果這100多位消費者不滿意，可以提出申訴，也呼籲該公司請善盡企業責任。"},{"pid":"ebe2481d30bf6f8a32ffaf16e2b483b99b43bb3a","tid":2241321,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:47:34.000Z","msg":"雖然foodpanda提供補償，不過消保官強調，如果這100多位消費者不滿意，可以提出申訴，也呼籲該公司請善盡企業責任。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799cfcaec364503b2c8329498f68f6c9219c0a7d","tid":2241321,"uid":80866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"全額補償即係每支比返十幾蚊台幣你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b3b1d3bd0f33c2904ec851644375eeedf11f70","tid":2241321,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebe2481d30bf6f8a32ffaf16e2b483b99b43bb3a","tid":2241321,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:47:34.000Z","msg":"雖然foodpanda提供補償，不過消保官強調，如果這100多位消費者不滿意，可以提出申訴，也呼籲該公司請善盡企業責任。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:49:31.000Z","msg":"兇宅有次都標錯<br />\n咪又係cancel晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9752bdf39e5460dcc969f119428f409086694bbd","tid":2241321,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:51:38.000Z","msg":"錯價9成都唔出貨架LA.&nbsp;又唔係咩新鮮野.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n肯出貨就當賣廣告.&nbsp;不過retails多數睬你都on9."},{"pid":"136d139145d29374692526552a7891d6d5cf09dd","tid":2241321,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"799cfcaec364503b2c8329498f68f6c9219c0a7d","tid":2241321,"uid":80866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"全額補償即係每支比返十幾蚊台幣你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:44:45.000Z","msg":"foodpanda已向訂單被取消的消費者說明致歉，並提供全額退款與補償券，補償券為消費滿200元可立折200元的抵用券，優惠碼有效期限至2020年12月31且限訂購foodpanda生鮮雜貨使用，每人限用1次。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a235214baed07871c151946f90600978259036f","tid":2241321,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"成班乞丐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722ec001f5869f3df015081569ef102befdd3733","tid":2241321,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a235214baed07871c151946f90600978259036f","tid":2241321,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"成班乞丐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:48:13.000Z","msg":"上次 豐澤單野連登仔屌爆誠仔<br />\n你快d走"},{"pid":"be56544c58ccdb4be9644ff890928302a612edb3","tid":2241321,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"但國泰頭等就應數"},{"pid":"20710f0c776038992a35028f3607ca0c0f83fdb6","tid":2241321,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be56544c58ccdb4be9644ff890928302a612edb3","tid":2241321,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"但國泰頭等就應數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T09:51:48.000Z","msg":"*認數"},{"pid":"5a62fbe658fc53a10d60e1b643e40f97b945736f","tid":2241321,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9752bdf39e5460dcc969f119428f409086694bbd","tid":2241321,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:51:38.000Z","msg":"錯價9成都唔出貨架LA.&nbsp;又唔係咩新鮮野.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n肯出貨就當賣廣告.&nbsp;不過retails多數睬你都on9."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:17:18.000Z","msg":"佢話有出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />部分無貨"},{"pid":"b91f01f32d628f420eb53f8b0e1d57d69c43f628","tid":2241321,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T10:49:13.00